Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}思維慌亂手足無措
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}最後大聲對我說
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}「我喜歡你」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}你我會陷入怎樣的戀情
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}將由我們共同探究
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}我早已失了方寸
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}每當被你深情凝視
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}內心顫動不已
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,200)}快將口是心非的我帶走吧
